Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:30.00,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}コートなんていらない　帽子もね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:37.82,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}シャーペンの芯だけ履いて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:45.35,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}くるる　くるる　く　駆け抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:52.99,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}くるる　くるる　く　足跡は×印だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:59.87,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}校舎の壁　突き抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:08.15,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}どこにも行ける　そこに道がある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:15.43,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)} スカートのひだ　乱れない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:22.97,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,800)}秘密の旅なら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:15.21,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}把白色的地图  完全展开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:22.09,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}快去  藏起宝箱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:30.00,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不用穿外套  也不用戴帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:37.82,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只要带着装上笔芯的自动铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:45.35,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}kururu  kururu  ku  飞奔过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:52.99,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}kururu  kururu  ku  把足迹画上×
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:59.87,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}穿过校舍的墙壁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:08.15,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}通向四方的路  就在脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:15.43,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}裙子的折痕是不会乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:22.97,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,800)}假如这是秘密的旅行的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:45.84,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}街の彩りさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:51.36,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}どことなく淋しげな　冬の景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:55.40,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}背中見せ駆けていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:58.18,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}あなたを思う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.09,0:23:07.94,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}二人の間には　透明な四角形
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.95,0:23:17.33,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今は霞んでる　ため息の結晶で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.85,0:23:21.90,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}窓ガラス　窓ガラス
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.91,0:23:27.90,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}くもってて　あなたが見えないの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:33.89,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}そこにいることは　わかっているのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:37.90,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}笑ってる？　泣いてるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:43.93,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}しかめっ面てもいいから　見せて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:52.89,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,800)}そちらの方からも　ガラスを拭いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:45.84,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}斑斓街道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:51.36,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}都不禁染上寂寞的冬日景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:55.40,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}想起当年的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:58.18,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}是如此的逞能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.09,0:23:07.94,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在两人中间有着透明的四角形
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.95,0:23:17.33,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}因为叹气的结晶  如今变得雾霭茫茫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.85,0:23:21.90,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}窗上的玻璃  窗上的玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.91,0:23:27.90,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}雾气朦胧让我看不清你的轮廓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:33.89,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}虽然明知你就在对面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:37.90,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你在笑？还是在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:43.93,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}哪怕是眉头紧锁也让我看一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:52.89,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,800)}你也从对面擦擦玻璃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.69,0:02:05.70,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,平淡的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到莉莉安学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能出示您的入场券吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  请让我看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安  欢迎来到莉莉安学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.57,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（藤松缘日村）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是二年松组的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卖啊卖啊  卖光光吧  哦～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学  为什么不跟着喊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学你真是干劲十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是手术后的第一个学园祭  兴奋是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到藤松缘日村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,学园祭当天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.97,0:02:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学和我担任二年藤组松组两班联手举办的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,藤松缘日村叫卖员的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来想当店员的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}要不要来份棉花糖呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}藤松縁日村在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蓉子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨～久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:03:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么晚才来  圣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要让人等多久你才开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,江利子还没来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打了个电话  说是不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说是如果出现得太频繁  由乃就太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,江利子有那么常到高中部来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我也没听说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快下来  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我无论如何也要进去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是何许人也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样说话很失礼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没想拿你怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是来建议你  翻墙是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:03:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,圣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.47,0:04:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蔷薇大人风范还在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请留步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我是这里一个学生的家属
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,家属？那入场券呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该清楚没有入场券是不能进入莉莉安学园祭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果忘了带  到受理处说出该学生的姓名和班级就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道她所在的班级
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是细川夕子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子…很像一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盛况空前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学  我走开一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  这是我的社团经营的店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？那可要去打声招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可南子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的入场券还剩这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有给家人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我先告辞了  一会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,缘日村真是生意兴隆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也要两份关东煮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  请稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子  给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,方便的话去尝一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啦  我请你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候只要说「承蒙款待」就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有理由要您请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,理由…理由是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当作是帮我们演话剧的回礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我一会儿还想去你们班的展台看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那到时候我会给您带路的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到祐巳同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快来快来  这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,表现出「请尝这美味关东煮」的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学站着别动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学  刚刚的客人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部交给真美同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来  拿好法兰克香肠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并排站着摆好姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笑得开心点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:07:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子同学太棒了  白蔷薇大人的浴衣装绝对很赞！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在捞水球前拍张照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思了  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说是要把照片放在莉莉安瓦版
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是摄影部和新闻部嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一整天都会这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个卷发的一年级生去了别的地方咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚过来看到你在忙就先离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还说了声「承蒙款待」这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…姐姐大人现在在负责自己的班级…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在她换班前先去展台看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来应该可以一起去看瞳子的演出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  您没受伤吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  刚才我太急了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您才是  没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您关心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  请问  这附近有电话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关东煮？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关东煮的话  那边的拐角往前走就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:23.63,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：这里祐巳把电话「おでんわ」听成了关东煮在哪「おでんは…」。）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蓉子大人  圣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  就觉得跟谁很像来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子很像祐巳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是相貌  是感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,进学校前在路上捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍不注意就让她跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很像…是猫吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:09.24,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：因为圣说了「捡到的」，所以祐巳以为是猫。）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳是要去祥子班里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来带路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请往这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她所指的…难道是电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  什么事都没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是她当班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  她去保健室了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是身体出问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是被荣子老师叫去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们等到她回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跳起来拿糖果的垂直跳跃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和能拿巧克力的反复横跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:09:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳  我们来比一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可南子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请加我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在追我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  请装作没事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关东煮…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是夕子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帮了我大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,意外地遇到不想见的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一逃开  对方就追了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子  你有客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问是去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,边走边说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳也过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来好像很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉  您们专程过来却…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意  我们刚好也有事要办了  一会儿再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才保健老师把我叫过去  说是父亲过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是父亲昨天因为工作关系去纽约了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然觉得是搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是去了趟保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人不是我父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那姐姐大人为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他拿着写有我名字的入场券
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以老师才会弄错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人的入场券…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子是优给他的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柏木学长吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说是对方进不了学园祭正感到为难
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说他为了见女儿特意从新舄过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可南子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  在里面的人就是可南子的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想见他  就自己走进去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会勉强你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…有时可能一生都不能再相见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:13:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候再后悔没有说出心里话就晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲是哪里不舒服吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说他进来保健室时脸色惨白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,问能不能借床躺一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没撒谎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可南子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸最差劲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全是爸爸的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是和妈妈离婚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不能说好出戏剧的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就连夕子学姐的事也一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是爸爸把夕子学姐的人生弄得一团糟！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你爸爸的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐居然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直想和可南子谈谈的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你一直避开我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我升入高中就因车祸受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,医生让我停止打篮球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在我迷茫的时候  我想起了细川教练
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想说如果是曾因身体原因引退的教练
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就能理解我的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,此后两人变得常见面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的我喜欢上了可南子的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢…上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当初如果不逃避说出来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算得不到原谅  就算会被憎恨也该说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可南子的爸爸太出色了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不禁心动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却让可南子因为我倍受伤害…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…可南子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我是明白的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸实现了妈妈想继续工作的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸离开家也是基于妈妈的工作压力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,离婚是双方互相商谈后做出的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可南子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可南子之所以会讨厌男生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是认为爸爸毁了她最喜爱的学姐的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以无法原谅他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可南子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:16:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可南子  已经没有心结了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚在这里换了尿布
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…来保健室的原因是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是可南子的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫次子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱抱她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大团圆收场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我们也去哪里转转吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  还不到一点半
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  「若草物语」已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎么这么着急？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有个帮山百合会演出的一年级生  要在戏剧社的舞台上表演
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个电钻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西  烧掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你这个粗鲁的人  这是一本很重要的书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子饰演的艾美  栩栩如生十分完美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,时而狂妄自大  时而固执己见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把可爱的艾美演得充满魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以稍微晚一点再去后台准备吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子  你演得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明迟到了还好意思说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  你察觉到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但我在你说第一句台词前赶到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要换衣服了请让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子脱下这身就直接换上「深宫幽情」的戏服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那干脆就这么出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是约好了嘛  给我带路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现…现在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学…？还有瞳子也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  瞳子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么约定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}姐姐大人～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}把脸抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山百合会版「深宫幽情」在爆笑中开场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是多么的幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两位妻子为我生下了一龙一凤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可爱的孩子们像极了妻子们  十分俊俏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然南可子还是不能把台词流畅地说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但比起之前  表情已经舒缓一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每年的后夜祭你总是一个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后姐姐大人每年都会一定能找到我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妨碍到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们散散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们结为姐妹刚好是一周年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳  我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚本来不想做什么特殊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不像你的生日或白色情人节那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想做些什么却又无从着手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说  并没有什么「只有今天是特别的」的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不论明天还是后天  祐巳都是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来都是  接下去的日子也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说今天一点都不特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟昨天没有区别  只是平淡的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白我说的意思吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这番话使我豁然开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:38.08,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：「目から鳞がはがれて落ちる」原本眼睛被鱼鳞遮住，\N而障蔽视线，掉下来就是豁然开朗，跟后面的眼泪双关。）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都流下眼泪来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个小笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.06,0:22:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你去认个妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人这个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.70,0:22:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一边说着今天是平淡的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却在结为姐妹一周年的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我下了一道难题
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乃梨子已经有了学姐般的威严了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.88,0:24:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？令大人  没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.04,0:24:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢  我妹妹还像个小孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.31,0:24:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我妹妹也一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,令大人  祥子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.31,0:24:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果由乃同学和祐巳同学都找到妹妹  自然会稳重起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.45,0:24:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.82,0:24:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还不好说？姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.91,0:24:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁给我施加压力让我找个妹妹的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.39,0:24:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一回  「妹妹甄选会」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.74,0:24:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底该怎么认妹妹啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.45,0:24:35.38,biaoti1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\pos(543,285)}妹 妹 甄 选 会
